description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Potomac, which features a new look from Robyn, Monique's live podcast, and a Wendy event. After Potomac, Danny hops into the world of The Bachelorette with some thoughts on the first two episodes. Are we supposed to like Claire? Why did ABC censor the butts? So many questions.


RHOP Recap: 6:36ish

The Bachelorette: 27:42ish


PS Subscribe to Danny's spinoff podcast, A Very Merry Iconic Podcast, which launches season 2 on October 28!
